content: I went in expecting this app to be super minimalist and it is that - you will need to be an experienced hot yoga practitioner to be able to use it at all. I was fine with that - I'm looking for a minimalist way to practice at home. Unfortunately this app is also super buggy. Try and turn down the background music? The voice queues go away. Skip a pose? The voice queues go away. There's also no way to customize to do single sets, or make a custom program which seems obvious.
My experience is perfect. Love this app.it is much more efficient to use this app then drive through traffic for 40 minutes and join inexpensive yoga studio and possibly catch Covid. Come on!
Some of the postures are not healthy for the neck and back ðŸ¤¨
replyContent: Hi, we are sorry that did not enjoy the app so much. These are the standard Bikram postures and the app is specific to this practice, nothing additional is added.

content: Pathetic service. Keeps hanging and no instructions !
replyContent:
I am sorry to see you are having issues.  We have released an update that addresses hanging issues.  Also, there is a voice coach that provides instructions.

If you are still having problems, then please let us know using the in-app "Contact Us" button.

Best Regards,
